论以保护所有人。”</p><p> Boomtown 2025  - 以前被称为“第4章：现在的力量”  - 将看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sean-paul">Sean Paul，Sean Paul，</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sex-pistols">性手枪</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-carter">Frank Carter</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maribou-state">Maribou State</a> ，Maribou State， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/overmono">Overmono</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hybrid-minds">Hybrid Minds</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a> ，Nia Archives， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/azealia-banks">Azealia Banks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rudimental">Rudim3ntal</a>在音乐节上表演。</p><p> Boomtown后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boomtown-survives-official-review-after-mans-death-and-local-complaints-3835126">Boomtown在人类去世后将官方审查幸存下来，当地投诉</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
